{"tid":2496443,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《全民造星III》馬拉Karen加盟《天盟娛樂》做陳展鵬小師妹：想同佢合唱！","createTime":"2021-04-19T23:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T10:21:11.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"65aeb8aa722d31ff9d76aa85dde74cc5fcb21d5b","tid":2496443,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T23:48:34.000Z","msg":"龔柯允（Karen）今日（19/4）現身九展舉行記者會，宣佈正式加盟《天盟娛樂》。Karen表示：「其實我今日嘅心情激動又興奮。因為要追夢，不經不覺留喺香港已經11年，當中經歷過好多辛酸。但當我諗起而家企喺呢度簽咗一間公司，加入咗《天盟娛樂》呢個大家庭，令到成件事都充滿盼望，所以令我剛才喺台度爆喊。（做視帝陳展鵬師妹感覺如何？）好開心可以同視帝展鵬同一間公司，如果可以我都想同佢合唱歌曲，亦都希望能夠同公司所有型男歌手一齊大合唱。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210419/460928808980058112978014.jpeg/y6eas2M-cAYLb6JTFGz1g5CczHlyp-WG84ZxffOGcX0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210419%2F460928808980058112978014.jpeg%2Fy6eas2M-cAYLb6JTFGz1g5CczHlyp-WG84ZxffOGcX0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=e1265000&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210419/460927953841426432143086.jpeg/Te065ASEG7dJpYpfEfWTQppt0WLdnGwmOSHxzzkh8c8?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210419%2F460927953841426432143086.jpeg%2FTe065ASEG7dJpYpfEfWTQppt0WLdnGwmOSHxzzkh8c8%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=ca4a0c75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d407b281f875dbc9550eda545d43db016476e4c","tid":2496443,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T00:08:37.000Z","msg":"即係會上TVB?"},{"pid":"d62f75f2bb004144c29c52273c2f9dca54715550","tid":2496443,"uid":52874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T00:11:50.000Z","msg":"佢每次海豚音都諗起音波泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下下都出大技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57215f36ef02383b35db93f63a0f4c8a58f83ec","tid":2496443,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d407